CustomField.description: The GeoResults assigned code to indicate the current Portability Status of the 10 digit telephone number. A code of "0" indicates that this 10 digit telephone number is not currently ported. A code of "1" indicates that this individual 10 digit telephone number is currently ported.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: A code of "0" indicates that this 10 digit telephone number is not currently ported. A code of "1" indicates that this individual 10 digit telephone number is currently ported.
CustomField.label: Portability Status Indicator Code
